headline.print_headline: Ex-President Gbagbo's Party Withdraws From Ivory Coast Poll Body
headline.main: Ex-President Gbagbo's Party Withdraws From Ivory Coast Poll Body

lead_paragraph: The party of former Ivory Coast President Laurent Gbagbo withdrew from the country's election commission on Sunday, setting back efforts to draw it into the political mainstream before a scheduled presidential election next year.
